							was about to attempt it, he fell, &amp; all his
							strength was taken from him, so that he
							could neither move a limb, nor speak
							a word, till I came. I spoke comfortably
							to him, encouraging him to take his
							refuge to our Saviour &amp; conducting him
							to his room, I prayed with him, &amp; in the
							sequel he grew better. The other person
						
