							<l>Who obtain'd the victory,</l>
							<l>Thro' the blood of Christ alone;</l>
							<l>That we may most zealously,</l>
							<l>Imitate their constancy,</l>
							<l>Till we too the prize receive,</l>
							<l>And with them in glory live! </l>
